title: Microsoft CEO says Google’s deals with Apple led to its dominance
description: At Google’s antitrust trial, Microsoft’s Satya Nadella said Google’s search engine is dominant because of its deals making it the default option across devices.

title: Once seen as the future, Boeing struggles to make a case for Starliner
description: Says the executive in charge of the program, “Probably the biggest challenge I have is defining how do I make this into a positive business case, given the market conditions as we see them right now.”

title: 8 ways to combat ageism in your job search
description: Expert advice for how to avoid negative stereotypes associated with younger and more mature workers.
